name: TuftsDining
0: ”Alexa, ask Tufts Dining are there tendies?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tufts dining
des: A skill that checks if Chicken Tenders (tendies) are being served at Tufts University. If there are tendies, Alexa tells you which hall they're being served in. Just say "Ask Tufts Dining are there tendies?"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
